The entire code is in the files main.cpp, stego.cpp and stego.h
The CImg.h is the CImg library code.

To compile use "make"
To run use "./stego" and follow the options.
For input images, you may use "cover.jpg" and "secret.jpg" present in the same folder.

Current following options are supported:
1. Encrypt image into another image
2. Decrypt image
3. Encrypt text into an image
4. Decrypt text from an image
